item.description:
 &lt;h1 id=&#34;连背景都是特效的博客jelly&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#连背景都是特效的博客jelly&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 连背景都是特效的博客–Jelly&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A wonderful, elegant and eye-protected light theme for hexo. Adapted from two previous themes, &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2xpdHRlbi9oZXhvLXRoZW1lLXlpbGlh&#34;&gt;Yilia&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3NtYWNrZ2cvaGV4by10aGVtZS1zbWFja2Rvd24=&#34;&gt;smackdown&lt;/span&gt;, it has made lots of changes in the UI, fixed some bugs and added other features.&lt;/p&gt;
