&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;attr&#34;&gt;aboutme:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;I&amp;#x27;m&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;developer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Uncomment the lines that are commented out in the  &lt;code&gt;_config.yml&lt;/code&gt;  file according to your needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use  &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;!-- more --&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;  to specify which part to be revealed in the home page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add a  &lt;code&gt;.jpg&lt;/code&gt;  picture and rename it  &lt;code&gt;bg.jpg&lt;/code&gt;  and put it in the  &lt;code&gt;themes/jelly/source/img&lt;/code&gt;  as your background picture (must be that name, or you should change the name in the  &lt;code&gt;style.styl&lt;/code&gt;  file in the css directory).&lt;/p&gt;
